abstract: Commerce Department reports wholesale inventories grew 1.4 percent in October, compared with 0.5 percent rise in September, and biggest monthly gain since Oct 2011.
lead_paragraph: The increase is nearly triple the 0.5 percent gain in September and the biggest monthly gain since October 2011.

headline.main: Wholesale Inventories Rose 1.4% in October, Suggesting Businesses Expect Stronger Sales
